# How ScreenToKitchen Works

This note explains the app in plain language, but still covers the technical pieces so non-developers can understand what is happening.

---

## What this app does

You take a picture of a recipe, and the app:

1. Reads text from the image (OCR)
2. Sends that text to an AI conversion service
3. Shows a clean recipe (title, ingredients, steps, notes)
4. Lets you save it and browse saved recipes in a catalogue

